ack 6.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，可在防火墙上限制对端口 5555 的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并配置入侵检测规则监控异常连接数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-02/0387.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1015","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX0006-115","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19782","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1d6385d398a2a41185d3cc14943c25f73c724ba3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0179.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0179","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0179.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8b7c7b13d1542fc7ddfb9cf48e51f3de3ab5c4ab/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0179.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gmvx-gg98-qqwq/GHSA-gmvx-gg98-qqwq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0179.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001198.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c1026c7b-c5ef-4ab6-9b78-4c2cde57382f.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/280f76b10d0670f8b6c2dcb23b3656450c8b6abc/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0157.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0157.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0157.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0156","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0156.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0178","title":"Foundry Networks ServerIron TCP 序列号预测漏洞","description":"Foundry Networks 公司 ServerIron 系列交换机存在 TCP/IP 序列号可预测漏洞。由于设备在生成 TCP 初始序列号时使用了可预测的算法或固定模式，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过分析网络流量推断出序列号，进而伪造 TCP 会话数据包实施会话劫持或欺骗攻击。该漏洞可导致攻击者冒充可信主机与目标设备建立连接，绕过访问控制策略，获取敏感信息或执行未授权操作。受影响设备为 ServerIron 系列交换机，攻击者需处于同一网络路径上才能实施有效攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0178"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:09.800","remediation":"升级 ServerIron 交换机固件至厂商修复版本，启用 TCP 序列号随机化功能。如无法升级，建议在网络边界部署 IPS/IDS 设备检测会话劫持行为，并对关键管理会话启用 IPsec 或 SSH 加密传输以防止欺骗攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.foundrynet.com/bugTraq.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1017","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d25d3aeab9dc76030f155f9e202a4a7c294f86bf/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0178.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0178","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0178.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0178.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xwch-qpr5-vp62/GHSA-xwch-qpr5-vp62.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0178.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--850699b2-b4a4-44b3-855a-67222684f5a8.owl","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-2000.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0156.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0606","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0606.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0187","title":"Alex Heiphetz Group eZshopper 3.0 loadpage.cgi 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Alex Heiphetz Group 开发的 eZshopper 3.0 电子商务软件中 loadpage.cgi CGI 脚本存在目录遍历与远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过在 URL 参数中使用 `..`（点点）路径遍历手法读取服务器上任意文件，或通过 shell 元字符注入执行任意系统命令。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响 eZshopper 3.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商至今未发布官方补丁，建议用户停止使用该软件或通过 Web 服务器访问控制限制 CGI 脚本的访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0187"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:10.903","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，无官方补丁可用。建议立即从 Web 服务器中删除或禁用 loadpage.cgi 脚本，并在 Apache/Nginx 中配置访问控制规则拒绝访问 /cgi-bin/ 目录下的 .cgi 文件。如业务仍依赖该软件，建议迁移至仍在维护的替代电商平台，或使用 WAF 规则拦截包含 ../ 及 shell 元字符的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-02/0356.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1014","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19781","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1d6385d398a2a41185d3cc14943c25f73c724ba3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0187.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0187","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0187.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/baa4573f2fa6813cfbc3f5cda2f1796a92d64bdf/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0187.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j9g5-5989-hfr7/GHSA-j9g5-5989-hfr7.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0187.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1014/info.html","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001194.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0606.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0184","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0184.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0209","title":"Lynx 浏览器缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Lynx 2.x 浏览器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造包含超长 URL 的恶意网页，诱使用户访问后触发缓冲区溢出，导致 Lynx 崩溃，并可能利用该漏洞在目标系统上执行任意命令。攻击条件为受害者使用 Lynx 浏览器访问攻击者控制的恶意页面。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0209"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-27","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"升级 Lynx 浏览器至 2.8.5 或更高版本，避免访问不可信来源的超长 URL 链接，或使用其他更安全的浏览器替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T03:04:03.026500538+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1012","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2000-0209"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0184.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0149","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0149.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0170","title":"Red Hat Linux man 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"RedHat Linux 6.1 man 程序缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0170"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:08.797","remediation":"升级 man 软件包至修复版本（如 man-1.5i-3 及以上），或安装 RedHat 官方提供的安全补丁 RHSA-2000:017。临时缓解措施：限制本地用户设置 MANPAGER 环境变量的权限，或使用 chmod 去除 man 程序的 setuid 位（将导致手册页格式化功能受限）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1011","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/255","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0170.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/11cd4f8209787c7c31fa82c66038f34b2ebde042/2000/CVE-2000-0170.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/90a8399ddd69cc2b4891beb4fe35c5ac0c17dcb1/2000/CVE-2000-0170/paper.txt","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0170","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/3ff60d1369c5ce67d5eb51a05949843ecdda5b5d/2000/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8b7c7b13d1542fc7ddfb9cf48e51f3de3ab5c4ab/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0170.json","https://github.com/diannaofengzi/POC/blob/14d504f7488db9229f6f02be54aab53e3cfee0dc/databases/2000/database/CVE-2000-0170/README.md","https://github.com/0xT11/CVE-POC/blob/2b6f11c3712c0efb88ac3edeab3d0aafa1f7a090/2000/CVE-2000-0170.json","https://github.com/CVEhive/CVEhive/blob/b9915233fd01050601434cf4b7a2b0f95536073b/data/CVE-2022-31813/repo/2000/CVE-2000-0170/paper.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/mike182/exploit"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0149.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0149.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0149.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0196","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0196.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0221","title":"北电网络 Nautica Marlin SNMP服务拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Nortel Networks Nautica Marlin 桥接设备（交换机）的 SNMP 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。该设备在处理送往 SNMP 端口（UDP 161）的 UDP 数据包时，未能正确处理长度为零的畸形数据包。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标设备的 SNMP 端口发送一个零长度的 UDP 数据包，即可触发该缺陷，导致设备 SNMP 服务崩溃或设备停止正常转发，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响运行相关固件的 Nautica Marlin 桥接设备，攻击条件简单，无需认证且可远程利用，属于典型的可用性破坏型漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0221"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:15.397","remediation":"建议升级 Nortel Nautica Marlin 桥接设备至厂商发布的安全固件版本（具体版本号请向 Nortel 技术支持确认并刷入最新补丁）。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙或 ACL 上过滤发往设备 SNMP UDP 端口（161）的畸形零长度 UDP 报文，并仅允许受信任管理网段访问 SNMP 服务，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1009","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19766","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0221.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0221","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0221.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0221.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/279.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/dos.rules","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0221.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.190","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0196.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0187","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0187.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0212","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9094,\"outputTokens\":22,\"totalTokens\":10844}}","description":"Pragma Systems InterAccess TelnetD Server 4.0 在处理终端客户端配置信息（terminal client configuration）时存在缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标 Telnet 服务发送特制的畸形终端配置数据，触发服务异常并导致拒绝服务（DoS），使 Telnet 守护进程崩溃或拒绝后续连接。该漏洞影响运行 InterAccess TelnetD Server 4.0 的 Windows 系统，攻击条件为攻击者能够与目标服务器的 Telnet 端口（默认 23）建立网络连接。利用方式简单，仅需发送畸形配置报文即可造成服务不可用，CVSS 评分约 5.0，危害等级为中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0212"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:14.190","remediation":"建议升级 Pragma Systems InterAccess TelnetD Server 至 4.0 之后的修复版本（建议升级至 5.0 或更高版本），可从 Pragma Systems 官网下载最新补丁。如暂时无法升级，建议在防火墙层面限制 Telnet 服务（TCP 23 端口）仅允许可信 IP 访问，或在不影响业务前提下暂时禁用 Telnet 服务改用 SSH 替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1001","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4033","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19760","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d69ab21f83909859ed75ab8ba3287f9f633b856f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0212.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0212","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0212.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c9ec7f26a52f816468b636e23146049097db5070/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0212.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m62v-fp25-jhj4/GHSA-m62v-fp25-jhj4.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0212.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001189.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0a9bf5c7-b9b4-44ea-9210-9bcf151b9287.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0187.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0171","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0171.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0194","title":"Corel Linux OS 1.0 buildxconfig 本地任意文件修改漏洞","description":"Corel Linux OS 1.0 中的 buildxconfig 工具存在任意文件写入漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 buildxconfig 传递 -x 或 -f 参数，以 root 权限修改或创建系统任意文件，从而覆盖关键配置文件或植入恶意脚本，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 Corel Linux OS 1.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0194"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:11.867","remediation":"建议立即升级 Corel Linux OS 至 2.0 或更高版本，或移除 buildxconfig 的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/buildxconfig），限制仅 root 用户执行。如无法升级，可删除 buildxconfig 文件或限制其可执行权限为仅 root（chmod 700 /usr/bin/buildxconfig）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-02/0323.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1007","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19764","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1d6385d398a2a41185d3cc14943c25f73c724ba3/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0194.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0194","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0194.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/baa4573f2fa6813cfbc3f5cda2f1796a92d64bdf/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0194.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-58wc-vc65-8m9v/GHSA-58wc-vc65-8m9v.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0194.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a8df9188-433b-4932-8107-b720e82aaa9c.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/b2f46398fe44a78cde72b37ec1d56278cb4dcc92/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0171.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0192","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0192.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0217","title":"OpenSSH X11转发远程会话劫持漏洞","description":"SSH默认配置启用了X11转发功能，允许远程攻击者通过恶意的xauth程序控制客户端的X会话，实现会话劫持。攻击者需要能够访问目标网络并诱使用户连接恶意X服务器，利用条件较为复杂但危害严重，可导致敏感信息泄露和远程控制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0217"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-24","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"禁用SSH的X11转发功能，在sshd_config中设置X11Forwarding no；或升级到修复此漏洞的SSH版本，限制xauth程序的执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-11-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1006"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0192.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0189","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0189.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0214","title":"FTPx FTP Explorer 1.0.00.10 弱密码加密漏洞","description":"FTPx FTP Explorer 1.0.00.10 版本在存储 FTP 站点的用户名、密码及配置文件时采用了弱加密算法，导致本地攻击者可通过访问存储配置文件或注册表项，利用弱加密算法解密还原明文凭据，从而窃取 FTP 站点登录凭证。该漏洞影响 FTPx FTP Explorer 1.0.00.10 版本，攻击者需具备本地文件系统或注册表访问权限，通过逆向分析弱加密算法或使用现成解密工具即可还原凭据，进而实施横向移动或数据窃取攻击。CVSS 评分 4.6，属中等严重程度漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0214"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-24","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议立即停止使用 FTPx FTP Explorer 1.0.00.10 并迁移至支持强加密存储的现代 FTP 客户端（如 FileZilla、WinSCP 等）；删除注册表 HKCU\\Software\\FTP Explorer\\Profiles\\ 下存储的所有站点配置，避免残留凭据被解密；若必须继续使用旧版本，请勿保存密码并改用外部密码管理器管理凭据。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1003","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.10.10002242035500.30645-100000%40unreal.sekure.org","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19762","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d69ab21f83909859ed75ab8ba3287f9f633b856f/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0214.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0214","https://github.com/nbrito/research/blob/f070ce78f917d962de8df74cc7a841f1cbbcfa00/cve/CVE-2000-0214/main.c","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0214.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c9ec7f26a52f816468b636e23146049097db5070/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0214.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c5m3-8qfv-wr54/GHSA-c5m3-8qfv-wr54.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1003/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0214.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152200_152300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0189.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0194","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0194.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0219","title":"Red Hat Linux 6.0 单用户模式身份验证绕过本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.0 单用户模式存在身份验证绕过漏洞，攻击者拥有物理访问权限或控制台访问权限时，可在系统启动进入单用户模式的密码提示界面按下 Ctrl+C 组合键，绕过 root 密码验证直接获取 root Shell 权限。该漏洞源于单用户模式密码验证逻辑缺陷，未正确处理中断信号，导致本地攻击者可提权至 root 权限，完全控制受影响系统。影响范围限于 Red Hat Linux 6.0 版本，攻击条件要求攻击者具备物理或控制台访问权限并能重启系统进入单用户模式，CVSS 评分 7.2，属高危本地提权漏洞。Red Hat 已发布补丁修复此漏洞，建议升级至修复版本或限制物理访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0219"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-23T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:15.137","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Red Hat Linux 6.1 或以上版本，该版本修复了单用户模式鉴别漏洞。如无法立即升级，可通过修改启动配置文件禁用单用户模式，或在 bootloader 中设置密码保护单用户模式进入，并确保 console=tty（禁用控制台重定向），以防止通过按 Ctrl+C 绕过认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1005","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=200002230248.NAA19185%40cairo.anu.edu.au","https://kc.mcafee.com/corporate/index?page=content&id=SB10053","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19763","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0219.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0219.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0219","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0219.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0219.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g249-hvwf-7935/GHSA-g249-hvwf-7935.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0219.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/redhat_single_user_mode.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0194.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0194.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0188","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0188.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0213","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9153,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10842}}","description":"Sambar Server 4.2 Beta 7 在 CGI 目录下包含 ECHO.BAT 和 HELLO.BAT 批处理文件，未对用户输入的 Shell 元字符进行过滤，导致远程攻击者可通过向 CGI 接口提交包含命令注入载荷的请求，实现任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 Sambar Server 4.2 Beta 7 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，属中危漏洞。成功利用可导致服务器完全沦陷，攻击者可执行系统命令、窃取敏感数据或植入恶意代码。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0213"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-23T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:14.327","remediation":"建议升级到 Sambar Server 的最新官方版本（7.0.0 及以上），移除 CGI 目录中的所有 .bat 文件并删除已知 vulnerable 脚本。特殊情况下如无法立即升级，可通过 Web 服务器配置禁止 CGI 执行、限制 CGI 目录访问权限，以及部署 WAF 规则阻止 shell 元字符检测。如果硬件支持，可完全禁用 IIS CGI 支持以彻底修复此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z